def removeNthFromEnd(head, n):
    dummy = ListNode(0)
    dummy.next = head
    fast = slow = dummy
    for _ in range(n):
        fast = fast.next
    while fast.next:
        fast = fast.next
        slow = slow.next
    slow.next = slow.next.next
    return dummy.next
